snippet.title: Half Sword Devlog 00 - Active Ragdoll, Medieval Armor, Kickstarter
snippet.description:
We are representing our little dev team working on Half Sword the Medieval Fencing Simulator! This is our first of the series of devlogs! 
Please enjoy!
